queries.sql: SELECT `noticias`.`id` as `id`, `noticias`.`titulo` as `tituloNoticia`, `noticias`.`texto` as `texto`, `noticias_categorias`.`titulo` as `tituloCategoria`, `noticias`.`capa` as `capa`, `noticias`.`dataNoticia` as `dataNoticia`, `noticias`.`slug` as `slug`, `noticias`.`visualizacoes` as `visualizacoes` FROM `noticias` JOIN `noticias_categorias` ON `noticias`.`idCategoria` = `noticias_categorias`.`id` WHERE `status` = 1 AND `noticias`.`deleted_at` IS NULL ORDER BY `noticias`.`dataNoticia` desc LIMIT 3
